{"id": "ChIJL_vwrBxM2YARPgkVrSsWjnw", "rating": 4.9, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 10720, "displayName": {"text": "Ed Fernandez Restaurant Birrieria", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Simple spot with colorful seating serving dishes such as tacos, quesadillas & birria, a spicy stew.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJL_vwrBxM2YARPgkVrSsWjnw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psb2RqWkhVVTUyTWpSNWRFd3hRVkJyY1VsblkzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We found a spot on TikTok and we wanted to try it since we are in San Diego for less than 48 hours, so we drove about 20 minutes from downtown San Diego to this spot. There is parking across the street which made it a lot easier because the front parking is full. You can get some to go, the long lines move pretty quick. We decided to sit inside and we got our food less than 10 minutes.\n\nWe chose to get the quesabrria, crunchy and regular and the regular tacos with birria  and the consomé On the side. Well, it was the best birria I  had in so long definitely worth a drive.\n\nThe owner took some time and brought us some bean tacos on the house. They were equally tasty and so generous on  his part. Had a quick convo with his because they man was working, this place is non stop", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We found a spot on TikTok and we wanted to try it since we are in San Diego for less than 48 hours, so we drove about 20 minutes from downtown San Diego to this spot. There is parking across the street which made it a lot easier because the front parking is full. You can get some to go, the long lines move pretty quick. We decided to sit inside and we got our food less than 10 minutes.\n\nWe chose to get the quesabrria, crunchy and regular and the regular tacos with birria  and the consomé On the side. Well, it was the best birria I  had in so long definitely worth a drive.\n\nThe owner took some time and brought us some bean tacos on the house. They were equally tasty and so generous on  his part. Had a quick convo with his because they man was working, this place is non stop", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mariana Reeves", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115632233410448647229/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7Vr0Kw8p8BTMbdQewj_BWzD_6-Gi6kKn5QUZZ34zsI8qHxD34=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-29T19:50:58.259035773Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psb2RqWkhVVTUyTWpSNWRFd3hRVkJyY1VsblkzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psb2RqWkhVVTUyTWpSNWRFd3hRVkJyY1VsblkzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80d94c1cacf0fb2f:0x7c8e162bad15093e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJL_vwrBxM2YARPgkVrSsWjnw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kMGFHdEtaeTF3VERNd2FuUnBTMmx0ZEVVM1UyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "They are so nice here, and thats before I say anything about the food…. Which is amazing. I had 2 birrieria tacos, an order of consume, and a coke and my order always $15 before tip. Mr Fernandez came to my table to make sure my meal was amazing. They had my drink on the table waiting on me immediately after I ordered and paid at the register. Highly recommend a trip here! Gracias!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "They are so nice here, and thats before I say anything about the food…. Which is amazing. I had 2 birrieria tacos, an order of consume, and a coke and my order always $15 before tip. Mr Fernandez came to my table to make sure my meal was amazing. They had my drink on the table waiting on me immediately after I ordered and paid at the register. Highly recommend a trip here! Gracias!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Dustin Atkin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105792020157918623233/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvGv2_9Cq4q4OEAbEYEy2BUclGx8wV07J9CL307czCgR6fHQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-25T21:24:58.186040386Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kMGFHdEtaeTF3VERNd2FuUnBTMmx0ZEVVM1UyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kMGFHdEtaeTF3VERNd2FuUnBTMmx0ZEVVM1UyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80d94c1cacf0fb2f:0x7c8e162bad15093e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJL_vwrBxM2YARPgkVrSsWjnw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkdFdGaFlRV2hJYzJONlRqZGtUa2RJUjAxVWFIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "we peddled a total of 12 miles to and from and it was totally worth it. The bread on the torta was warm crunchy and buttery. The Birria was super delicious and cooked to perfection (if  there is something I hate is over cooked birria). The tendon in the Birria was absolutely delicious service was quick and super friendly. definitely will be coming back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "we peddled a total of 12 miles to and from and it was totally worth it. The bread on the torta was warm crunchy and buttery. The Birria was super delicious and cooked to perfection (if  there is something I hate is over cooked birria). The tendon in the Birria was absolutely delicious service was quick and super friendly. definitely will be coming back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "ANGEL RODRIGUEZ", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103954677595596841976/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKtEUcRG5nwlO4dbr_HqexfZD0bOczgjaS0QnUiV6vfiaVFGg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-20T19:50:50.007483862Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkdFdGaFlRV2hJYzJONlRqZGtUa2RJUjAxVWFIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkdFdGaFlRV2hJYzJONlRqZGtUa2RJUjAxVWFIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80d94c1cacf0fb2f:0x7c8e162bad15093e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJL_vwrBxM2YARPgkVrSsWjnw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWaE9WVkhVMk10VmtwRWJqQmZTak10YkdJdFJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I had an amazing experience at Fernandez! I've been coming here for 15 years, and the food is still just as delicious as ever. I absolutely love their birria, and my favorite meal is Combo #1. Of course, I had to place a to-go order as well!\nOne thing I really appreciate is that Mr. Fernandez always greets us personally, which makes every visit feel welcoming and special. Great food, great service, and a wonderful atmosphere. I highly recommend Fernandez to anyone looking for authentic, flavorful food!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I had an amazing experience at Fernandez! I've been coming here for 15 years, and the food is still just as delicious as ever. I absolutely love their birria, and my favorite meal is Combo #1. Of course, I had to place a to-go order as well!\nOne thing I really appreciate is that Mr. Fernandez always greets us personally, which makes every visit feel welcoming and special. Great food, great service, and a wonderful atmosphere. I highly recommend Fernandez to anyone looking for authentic, flavorful food!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Karen Guzman", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101750965525120170090/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5us5lrqW779iCYtA3fAJdYSWOt3hAdcftm-8QcSxlbELLdA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-06T14:00:58.113462955Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWaE9WVkhVMk10VmtwRWJqQmZTak10YkdJdFJtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWaE9WVkhVMk10VmtwRWJqQmZTak10YkdJdFJtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80d94c1cacf0fb2f:0x7c8e162bad15093e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJL_vwrBxM2YARPgkVrSsWjnw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSWlFYRkVPRWRTYjI5bU9UUkNXamxQWTNrdE5XYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It’s difficult to find the words to truly explain how good this food and experience was for our family. Amazing! It was busy on a Sunday, but there was a man to help us park. After we ordered and sat, the friendly server brought us drinks and then the amazing assortment of birria and birria tacos. I’m quite sure we have never before had food this good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It’s difficult to find the words to truly explain how good this food and experience was for our family. Amazing! It was busy on a Sunday, but there was a man to help us park. After we ordered and sat, the friendly server brought us drinks and then the amazing assortment of birria and birria tacos. I’m quite sure we have never before had food this good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mike Froehlke", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113691634194999382954/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgG7nSh0z_tPvdg_4NxLKe8Rn4uP75T2HD_em6pq2HZkgFUHsg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-27T02:13:58.309381337Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSWlFYRkVPRWRTYjI5bU9UUkNXamxQWTNrdE5XYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSWlFYRkVPRWRTYjI5bU9UUkNXamxQWTNrdE5XYxAB!2m1!1s0x80d94c1cacf0fb2f:0x7c8e162bad15093e"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJL_vwrBxM2YARPgkVrSsWjnw/photos/AWCwydg2MERehev4IJvMwK0E9LsRkv